quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  52,24,Iwo adzazunguliridwa ndi kutchingidwa bwino ndi anyamata awoawo amene adzawatumizira ngati kuti iwo anali ndolo zobisika
  52,25,Ndipo iwo adzafunsana wina ndi mnzake ndi kuyankhulitsana
  52,26,"Iwo adzati, “Kale ife tidali a mantha ndi mabanja athu.”"
  52,27,“Koma Mulungu wationetsera chisomo chake ndipo watipulumutsa ife ku chilango cha kumoto.”
  52,28,“Ndithudi ife tinali kumupempha Iye yekha. Ndithudi Iye ndiye Mwini chifundo ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha.”
  52,29,"Motero pitiriza kukumbutsa ndi kulalikira. Chifukwa cha chisomo cha Ambuye wako, iwe si ndiwe munthu wonyenga kapena wamisala"
  52,30,"Kapena iwo amati, “Ndi Mlakatuli, ife tili kuyembekezera kuti choipa chidze pa iye.”"
  52,31,"Nena, “Yembekezerani! Nanenso ndili mmodzi wa oyembekezera.”"
  52,32,Kodi ndi maganizo awo amene ali kumawauza izi kapena iwo ndi anthu amene amaswa malamulo mosadodoma
  52,33,"Kodi kapena iwo amati, “Iye wapeka yekha uthengawu? Iyayi! iwo alibe chikhulupiriro.”"
  52,34,Alekeni nawo abweretse mawu olingana ndi awa ngati iwo ali kunena zoona
  52,35,Kodi iwo adalengedwa popanda china chake kapena iwo ndiwo a Namalenga
  52,36,Kapena ndiwo amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi? Iyayi! iwo alibe chikhulupiriro chokhazikika
  52,37,Kodi ndiwo amene amasunga chuma cha Ambuye wako? Kapena iwo ndiwo a nkhanza amene ali ndi ulamuliro wonena chilichonse chimene afuna
  52,38,Kodi kapena iwo ali ndi njira yomvetsera zomwe zinali kunenedwa? Motero mulekeni kazitape wawo kuti apereke umboni wokwanira
  52,39,Kodi kapena Iye ali ndi ana aakazi okha pamene inuyo muli ndi ana aamuna
  52,40,Kodi kapena iwe uli kuwafunsa malipiro kotero kuti iwo apanikizidwa kwambiri ndi ngongole
  52,41,Kodi kapena ali ndi zobisika ndipo amazilemba
  52,42,Kodi kapena ali kukonza chiwembu? Koma iwo amene sakhulupirira ndiwo amene ali ndi chiwembu
  52,43,Kodi kapena ali ndi mulungu wina kupatula Mulungu weniweni? Mulungu alemekezeke kuposa zimene iwo amamufanizira nazo
  52,44,"Ndipo iwo akadaona gawo lina la kumwamba lili kugwa pansi ndipo iwo akadati, “Ndi mitambo youndana.”"
  52,45,Motero alekeni mpaka pamene iwo akumana ndi tsiku lawo limene iwo adzakomoka ndi mantha
  52,46,Tsiku limene chiwembu sichidzawathandiza china chilichonse ndipo chithandizo sichidzaperekedwa kwa iwo
  52,47,"Ndipo, ndithudi, onse amene amachita zoipa, kuli chilango china pa chilango ichi koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa"
  52,48,"Motero pirira podikira chiweruzo cha Ambuye wako, chifukwa ndithudi iwe uli kusamalidwa ndi Ife ndipo lemekeza Ambuye wako pamene uuka ku tulo"
  52,49,"Nthawi ya usiku, lemekeza ulemerero wake ndi pa nthawi yolowa nyenyezi"
  53,1,Ndi pali nyenyezi pamene ili kulowa
  53,2,M’bale wanu sadasochere kapena kuti ndi wolakwa
  53,3,Ndipo iye sayankhula zofuna zake
  53,4,Icho ndi chochita kuuzidwa kwa iye
  53,5,Iye adaphunzitsidwa ndi Iye amene ali ndi mphamvu
  53,6,"Wopanda chilema chilichonse, kotero adadzuka ndi kukhala wokhazikika"
  53,7,Pamene iye anali patali kwambiri mu mlengalenga
  53,8,Ndipo adasendera ndi kudza pafupi
  53,9,Ndipo adali pa mtunda wolingana kuponya mipaliro iwiri kapena kucheperapo
  53,10,Motero Iye adaulula Uthenga kwa kapolo wake kudzera mwa Gabriyele
  53,11,Mtima wake wa Mtumwi siudaname ponena zimene iye adaona
  53,12,Kodi inu mudzatsutsana naye pa zimene iye adaona
  53,13,Ndithudi iye adamuona iye pamene anali kutsika kachiwiri
  53,14,Pafupi ndi mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,15,Pafupi pake pali munda womwe ndi malo opumirako
  53,16,Ndipo chimene chimaphimba chidakuta mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,17,Maso ake sadayang’ane kumbali kapena kupyola muyeso
  53,18,Ndithudi iye adaona zizindikiro zazikulu kwambiri za Ambuye wake
  53,19,Kodi inu maganiza za Lat ndi Uzza
  53,20,Ndi Manat wachitatu wamkazi
  53,21,Kwa inu amuna ndipo kwa Iye akazi
  53,22,Ndithudi kumeneku ndiko kugawa kosalungama
  53,23,"Awa ndi mayina chabe amene inu mwapeka, inu ndi atate anu, amene Mulungu sadakulamuleni ndi pang’ono pomwe. Iwo amangotsatira nkhani zakumva chabe zimene mitima yawo imafuna pamene, ndithudi, kwadza kale kwa iwo ulangizi wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo"
  53,24,Kodi munthu angapeze zonse zimene amafuna
  53,25,Koma Mulungu ndiye Mwini moyo umene uli nkudza ndi moyo wakale